This paper deals with privacy-preserving data exchange in a decentralized marketplace using blockchain technology. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves distributed systems and blockchain, which fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The use of blockchain also involves data structures and algorithms, which fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also deals with data management and storage, which fall under cs.DB (Databases). Finally, the paper involves machine learning and decision making, which fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
